cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL

The paper proposes a conceptual framework for higher-order artificial neural networks and focuses on their application to learning spatial transformations of images. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the paper primarily deals with machine learning and computer vision, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories.
